<plot>A slice-of-life comedy, THE 3 LITTLE WOLFS centers on the three Wolf brothers (ages 26-31) and their overbearing, yet well-intentioned mother, Sarah (Tovah Feldshuh). The story unfolds as the Wolf family and friends gather at Sarah's home on Long Island for their annual Passover seder to commemorate their ancestors' 40-year odyssey across Egypt's deserts... which compared to this eventful evening, seems like a walk in the park.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?538267</url></doc>
